<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 - পৃষ্ঠা পাওয়া যায়নি</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8 0%, #d9e2ec 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      color: #333;
      perspective: 1000px;
    }
    .error-container {
      text-align: center;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 8rem;
      margin: 0;
      color: #1e90ff;
      text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #b3d7ff, 
                   8px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transform: translateZ(50px);
      animation: pulse 2s infinite alternate;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      transform: translateZ(30px);
    }
    a {
      position: relative;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #1e90ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.4);
      overflow: hidden;
      transform: translateZ(40px);
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
      transform: translateY(-3px) translateZ(40px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.6);
    }
    a:active {
      transform: translateY(1px) translateZ(40px);
    }
    a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        transparent 25%,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 50%,
        transparent 75%
      );
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    a:hover::after {
      opacity: 1;
      animation: shine 1.5s infinite;
    }
    
    /* Animations */
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0) rotateY(0deg);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-20px) rotateY(5deg);
      }
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0% {
        transform: translateZ(50px) scale(1);
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateZ(50px) scale(1.05);
      }
    }
    @keyframes shine {
      0% {
        background-position: 150% 150%;
      }
      100% {
        background-position: -50% -50%;
      }
    }
    
    /* Responsive adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 5rem;
        text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #b3d7ff, 
                     6px 6px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>দুঃখিত! আপনি যে পৃষ্ঠাটি খুঁজছেন তা খুঁজে পাওয়া যায়নি।</p>
    <a href="/">হোম পেইজে ফিরে যান</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>